286: ## Date Parsing
287: 
288: The email organization system uses intelligent date parsing (`lib/date-based-filter.mjs`) to classify event emails:
289: 
290: **Supported Formats:**
291: - ISO 8601: `2026-03-25`, `2026/03/25`
292: - US format: `03/25/2026`, `3/25/2026`
293: - Text format: `March 25, 2026`, `March 25` (infers year)
294: - Weekday patterns: `@ Mon, Mar 23`, `@ Friday Mar 22`
295: - Returns `null` for unparseable dates
296: 
297: **Classification:**
298: - Past events (date < today): archive from inbox, keep label
299: - Future events (date ≥ today): label and keep in inbox
300: - Unknown: marked for manual review
301: 
302: **Implementation Notes:**
303: - Pure function: does not mutate input dates
304: - Handles missing years by inferring current or next year
305: - Used by `mark-past-events-read.mjs` to auto-archive old events
